&lt;center&gt;&lt;b&gt;Halve&lt;/b&gt; is a stylish, two-column jekyll theme.&lt;/center&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This theme is Jekyll port of &lt;a href=&quot;http://vangeltzo.com/&quot;&gt;vangeltzo.com&lt;/a&gt; (by &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/srekoble&quot;&gt;Vangelis Tzortzis&lt;/a&gt;). I couldn’t stop myself to port this theme when I saw his site. And he kindly gave me permission to share this with you.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;iframe src=&quot;https://ghbtns.com/github-btn.html?user=TaylanTatli&amp;amp;repo=Halve&amp;amp;type=star&amp;amp;count=true&amp;amp;size=large&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; scrolling=&quot;0&quot; width=&quot;160px&quot; height=&quot;30px&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;installation-and-quick-usage&quot;&gt;Installation and Quick Usage&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Fork the &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/TaylanTatli/Halve/fork&quot;&gt;Halve repo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Edit &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;_config.yml&lt;/code&gt; file.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Edit &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;index.md&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Edit &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;_data/projects.yaml&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Add a logo with a small one to &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;images&lt;/code&gt; folder. (eg. &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;logo.png&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;logo-small.png&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Remove sample posts from &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;_posts&lt;/code&gt; folder and add yours.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Remove/Change sample images from &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;images&lt;/code&gt; folder.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Change repo name to &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;YourUserName.github.io&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;That’s all.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you want to make a &lt;strong&gt;Project Page&lt;/strong&gt;, you have to use &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;gh-pages&lt;/code&gt; branch. For &lt;strong&gt;Personal Page&lt;/strong&gt;; &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;master&lt;/code&gt; branch. More info &lt;a href=&quot;https://help.github.com/articles/about-github-pages-and-jekyll/#jekylls-build-process&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;preview&quot;&gt;Preview&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;third&quot;&gt;
    
    &lt;a href=&quot;/images/halve-home-image.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/images/halve-home-image.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
    
    &lt;a href=&quot;/images/post-image-halve-1.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/images/post-image-halve-1.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
    
    &lt;a href=&quot;/images/post-image-halve-2.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/images/post-image-halve-2.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
    
    &lt;figcaption&gt;Screenshots of Halve Theme&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;

